↓

Login Remembered

""")

# --------------------------------------------------
# LOCAL STORAGE
# --------------------------------------------------

st.header("1️⃣1️⃣ Local Storage")

st.markdown("""
Local Storage stores data permanently.

Data remains even after closing the browser.
""")

st.code("""

localStorage.setItem(

"name",

"John"

);

""", language="javascript")

st.code("""

localStorage.getItem(

"name"

);

""", language="javascript")

st.success("""
Data remains until manually removed.
""")

# --------------------------------------------------
# LOCAL STORAGE EXAMPLE
# --------------------------------------------------

st.header("1️⃣2️⃣ Real World Example")

st.markdown("""

Theme Preference

↓

Store in Local Storage

↓

Open Website Again

↓

Theme Restored
""")

# --------------------------------------------------
# SESSION STORAGE
# --------------------------------------------------

st.header("1️⃣3️⃣ Session Storage")

st.markdown("""
Session Storage exists only during the current browser session.
""")

st.code("""

sessionStorage.setItem(

"course",

"FSD"

);

""", language="javascript")

st.code("""

sessionStorage.getItem(

"course"

);

""", language="javascript")

st.success("""
Removed automatically when browser tab closes.
""")

